text.tspan: ▶ Basic race game where each players is starting from
the same position and has to finish the race as fast
▶ Serve as replacement for slow evaluation by human players
▶ Used to estimate fairness of given game level
▶ Trained by PPO (Proximal Policy Optimization) algorithm
to drive as best as possible
Different abilities (i.e. cars in our game)
▶ Are represented as vectors of numbers. Each
number corresponds to an angle at given point
